:::Starscream/Battera/Ramjet/Banzai-Tron/Hurricane/Hellbat/Wheeljack:::

Starscream: Alright then.
::He walks into the base with Battera following behind him::
~~~~~
Ramjet: Don't worry, i think we'll prove it to them fine!
~~~~~
::Banzai-Tron, Hurricane, and Hellbat walk out of the base::
Hurricane: I will be world champ!
Hellbat: Just give me a piece of our enemies!
Banzai-Tron: MAY THE DEVIL TAKE THEM ALL!
::The other two stare at him blankly::
Banzai-Tron: What?
::Banzai-Tron takes off and starts flying to the CF.  Hellbat transforms to 
jet mode and Hurricane gets in, and they head to the CF::
~~~~~
::Wheeljack thinks for awhile::
Wheeljack: Sure, lets go to the battle, our work here is done.
::He starts walking to the CF::

--part1_66.d6a9077.27f5d76e_boundary
